# --- Produção (Railway) ---
# O Railway define RAILWAY_ENVIRONMENT; com isso a API ativa redirecionamento HTTP→HTTPS
# (via X-Forwarded-Proto) e o cabeçalho Strict-Transport-Security.
# Inclua as origens HTTPS do front, por exemplo:
# CORS_ORIGINS=https://seu-front.up.railway.app,https://seu-backend.up.railway.app
#
# Uvicorn atrás de proxy (recomendado no Railway) para X-Forwarded-*:
# uvicorn app.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000 --proxy-headers --forwarded-allow-ips='*'
#
# Desativar redirecionamento HTTPS na API (raro):
# FORCE_HTTPS=false
